widgets_values:
Input Image =================================
Recommended parameters:
Denoise: 0.5
ControlNet Strength: 1.0
Steps: 18
Tile Size: 1024

Workflow Setup ==============================
Configure model, LoRAs, and optional prompt. The prompt does not need to describe your image.

Initial Upscale =============================
Upscales the image with an upscale model. Default is 4x upscale, then downscale by 50% to sharpen details.

Explanation of parameters and troubleshooting:
https://github.com/roblaughter/comfyui-workflows/blob/main/docs/upscale.md

Download nodes and models:
https://github.com/roblaughter/comfyui-workflows/

Model Optimizations =============================

FreeU adds coherence at the expense of detail. 
PAG adds detail at the expense of inference speed.
Select the LoRA to add to the text
Select the Wildcard to add to the text
